projects.name: Stock Price Prediction Using High Frequency Data
projects.description: Spearheaded the development of a Machine Learning Model utilizing Python and Machine Learning for precise prediction of future prices of Stocks. Achieved a remarkable average accuracy of 0.852, showcasing the effectiveness and accuracy of the solution in predicting future prices of NSE Index Stocks.

projects.name: Connectz - Chatting Application
projects.description: Collaborated on the creation of Connectz using MERN Stack technology focusing on frontend design to ensure an intuitive user experience. Led the testing efforts for Connectz, identifying and resolving bugs to ensure a seamless chatting application.

experiences.description: Learnt and Developed a Machine Learning model using AI technology to predict Mental Health of People with a precision rate of 80. Executed the 6-week internship focused on AI and Machine Learning Models. Enhanced Skills in Data Analysis, Model Building, and Model Evaluation Techniques.

Implemented Linear Regression, Decision Tree, K-Nearest Neighbors, Support Vector Machine (SVM), and Random Forest models using python on the NSE Index Historical Dataset to predict future price of the Stocks in the Index. Led the Research and Development on Stock Market Price Prediction with High Frequency Data during the Internship Period and achieved good results with better accuracy than the papers I referred while researching.
